{"id":256544,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/许纪霖-为什么我批评莫言？/","date":"2012-10-12T03:15:05Z","modified":"2012-10-16T07:58:46Z","title":"许纪霖 | 为什么我批评莫言？","content":"<p>@许纪霖：批评莫言需要理由， 以下是我的评论：《为什么我批评莫言？》：如果莫言只是孤案，其实他不值得认真对待，可悲的是他代表了当今知识分子的主流，我称之为“平庸的乡愿”。而“平庸的乡愿”，正是“平庸的恶”的帮闲。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/%e8%ae%b8%e7%ba%aa%e9%9c%96-%e4%b8%ba%e4%bb%80%e4%b9%88%e6%88%91%e6%89%b9%e8%af%84%e8%8e%ab%e8%a8%80%ef%bc%9f/71bcc28ejw1dxs7qixanrj/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-256545\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-256545\" title=\"\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/10/71bcc28ejw1dxs7qixanrj.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"435\" height=\"1153\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/10/71bcc28ejw1dxs7qixanrj.jpg 435w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/10/71bcc28ejw1dxs7qixanrj-113x300.jpg 113w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/10/71bcc28ejw1dxs7qixanrj-386x1024.jpg 386w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 435px) 100vw, 435px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18269,9203],"tags":[9050,20554,9524]}